summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of West Fifty-eight Street from Twentieth Avenue N.W. to Twenty-fourth Avenue N.W. in the City of Seattle, by regrading under Ordinance No. 18437, creating Local Improvement District No. 1737 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
